 Idemitsu TOP >  Products & Services >  LubricantsMarine OilsMaintenance OilsMetal Working OilsGrease ProductsIndustrial OilsTDF (Traction Drive Fluid) A traction drive fluid is a specialized lubricant for improving the operation of a continuously variable transmission.


PVE (Polyvinyl ether)


Polyvinylether is an innovative refrigeration oil developed by Idemitsu that offers several advantages for hydrofluorocarbon-based refrigerant systems.





PAG (Polyalkylene Glycol) Oil


Idemitsu is the world's leading manufacturer of polyalkylene glycol (PAG) oil, the primary lubricant used for automotive air conditioners.


