About Us
Idemitsu Lube India Private Limited is a leading manufacturer of Automobile and Industrial Lubricants in India. We bring to India our Technologically Advanced Lubricants from Japan with proven usage and track record.
We are 100% owned subsidiary of Idemitsu Kosan Company Limited, Japan (Fortune 500 Company), committed to 	provide environmentally friendly lubricants in India.
Idemitsu Lube India was established in India in 2006 as Sales & Marketing Company to provide Technical and Marketing support to our Japanese customers.
Our manufacturing plant located at Patalganga, Distt. Raigad, Maharashtra has state-of-the-art Blending, Filling & Packing facilities for manufacturing 	high-performance lubricants meeting global quality and product specifications.
Idemitsu is progressively working towards to provide environmentally friendly, high quality and technologically advanced lubricants to Indian Customers.
We manufacture wide range of Automotive Lubricants for 2 Wheelers, 4 Wheelers and Commercial Vehicles and have a very wide portfolio of Industrial Oils and speciality products like Turbine oils, Metal Working fluids, Quenching oils, etc.
We have a very strong Quality systems implemented in our Plant and are continuously innovating with high performance products keeping pace with advancements in technology and market needs.
We are of number of Supplier and Quality awards from various Automobile OEMs and continuously strive to create 	long lasting customer partnerships and provide world class customer service and quality.
