Welcome



Idemitsu Chemicals Europe Plc is the European subsidiary for Chemical products of Idemitsu Kosan Co., Ltd, a Japanese company which handles wide range of energy related business such as oil exploration, petroleum products, petrochemical products, electronic materials, coal, Uranium and Geothermal energy business.
"Move to a Higher Level" Idemitsu Chemicals Europe Plc is dedicated to providing customers with services based on technologies which generated Engineering plastics (Tarflon™, XAREC ™), Performance Chemicals (I-Marv, Linealene L-MODU), Electronic materials etc.
New application updated!
» Light Lens and Reflector in LED applications. Read more...















